was named for its small body size with the Latin word 
<taxonomicName box="[1156,1221,333,356]" class="Actinopterygii" family="Cyprinidae" genus="Metzia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Cypriniformes" pageId="5" pageNumber="231" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="parva">
<emphasis box="[1156,1221,333,356]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="231">parva</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(gender feminine) meaning small or little.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
